{"word":"G2434 - ἱλασμός - hilasmós - hil-as-mos' - Propitiation","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἱλασμός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>hilasmós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>hil-as-mos'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Propitiation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நிவர்த்தி செய்கிற கிருபாதார பலி - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. an appeasing, propitiating,"},{"paragraph":"2. the means of appeasing, a propitiation"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> <i>atonement</i>, that is, (concretely) an <i>expiator:</i> - propitiation."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2433 - ἱλάσκομαι - hiláskomai - hil-as'-kom-ahee/2433\">G2433</a>, <a href=\"#/G2434 - ἱλασμός - hilasmós - hil-as-mos'/2434\">G2434</a>, <a href=\"#/G2435 - ἱλαστήριον - hilastḗrion - hil-as-tay'-ree-on/2435\">G2435</a>, <a href=\"#/G2436 - ἵλεως - híleōs - hil'-eh-oce/2436\">G2436</a>"}]}